---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Generic.astro';
---

<Layout title='Season #6 - Pixel Craft - Pixel Series' backPage='/'>
  <div class="row justify-content-center">
    <h1 class="primary-title">Pixel Craft Season #6</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="col justify-content-center">
    <div class="col info text-center">
      <h2>Info</h2>
      <p>Season #6 of Pixel Craft this season we are starting in The Wild Update and playing in the same world for as long as we feel like keeping this world. We've also got a bunch of custom stuff that we are adding to the server to enhance our gameplay experience.</p>
      <p>We have an optional things for people to use if the want and one required thing. The optional things is a Fabric client. The required thing is a Custom Resource Pack that we use for the custom things that we wanted to add to the server. You can get all of these from <a class="external-links" href="https://download.pixilaremedia.com/user/pixilare-media/pixel-craft/season-6/resource-packs/" target="_blank">Resource Packs Here</a> and <a class="external-links" href="https://download.pixilaremedia.com/user/pixilare-media/pixel-craft/season-6/clients/" target="_blank">Clients Here</a>.</p>
      <p><a class="downloads" href="https://cdn.roebuck.dev/user/pixilare-media/pixel-series/pixel-craft/season-6/worlds/pixel-craft-season-6-starting-map.zip">Starting Map</a></p>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col"></div>
      <div class="col info text-center">
        <p>Some useful pages for this season.</p>
        <ul>
          <li><a class="internal-links" href="/pixel-craft/map/">Live Web Map</a></li>
          <li><a class="internal-links" href="/pixel-craft/season-6/shulker-box-advancements/">Shulker Box Advancements</a></li>
          <!--li><a class="internal-links" href="/pixel-craft/season-6/summoning-rituals/">Summoning Rituals</a></li-->
          <li><a class="internal-links" href="/pixel-craft/season-6/summoning-rituals/blood-moon/">Blood Moon Summoning Ritual</a></li>
          <li><a class="internal-links" href="/pixel-craft/season-6/item-combinations/">Item Combinations</a></li>
          <li><a class="internal-links" href="/pixel-craft/season-6/custom-items/">Custom Items</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="col"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .primary-title {
    border: 3px;
    border-color: lightslategray;
    border-style: groove;
